<md>Hi all! I'm helping several of my friends find software engineers (full time/intern) who want to join a Fintech startup. The company is an elite stealth software team creating artificial intelligence for the world's most renowned sovereign wealth funds. Attached below are the job descriptions: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IJkcDNBiQXdVw0zwlx34kbZVVRSdzM3o5aVImYrBetQ/edit?usp=sharing

They are hiring frontend/backend/ML engineers. If interested and you are a junior/senior/master who has related experiences or skills, please send a brief bio and your CV to tian1998@berkeley.edu. Thank you!</md>
